---
import SubPageLayout from '../layouts/SubPageLayout.astro';
---

<SubPageLayout
  title="Build Your Product — Step-by-Step Roadmap | Himanshu (@oye.nino)"
  description="A free, interactive 6-phase roadmap to take your product idea from zero to live — stack, MVP, deploy, domain, AI. By Himanshu (@oye.nino)."
  canonical="https://oyenino.com/roadmap.html"
  keywords="product roadmap, how to build a product, startup roadmap, MVP guide, deploy guide, tech stack guide, free roadmap, oye nino, Himanshu"
  needsTurnstile={true}
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>
  <div class="page-badge"><span class="pulse"></span> Free Roadmap</div>
  <h1>Build your product,<br /><em>step by step</em></h1>
  <p>Most products fail not because of bad code, but because of no plan. This roadmap gives you the exact 6 phases &mdash; from idea to live product &mdash; so you don't waste time figuring out what comes next.</p>
</section>

<!-- WHY A ROADMAP MATTERS -->
<div class="why-section" id="why-section">
  <div class="why-grid">
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">&#127919;</div>
      <h3>Clarity over chaos</h3>
      <p>Without a roadmap, you'll bounce between features, frameworks, and ideas. A plan keeps you shipping, not spiraling.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">&#9889;</div>
      <h3>Speed to launch</h3>
      <p>Knowing what to build first (and what to skip) saves weeks. An MVP with 3 features beats a half-done app with 20.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="why-card">
      <div class="why-icon">&#128176;</div>
      <h3>Zero to launch at &#8377;0</h3>
      <p>Every tool in this roadmap has a free tier. You don't need money to start &mdash; you need a plan and momentum.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- HOW TO PLAN -->
<div class="tips-section" id="tips-section">
  <div class="tips-title">Before you write code, <em>answer these</em></div>
  <ul class="tips-list">
    <li><div class="tip-num">1</div><div><strong>Who is your user?</strong> Not "everyone." One specific person with one specific problem. The narrower, the better.</div></li>
    <li><div class="tip-num">2</div><div><strong>What's the one thing it does?</strong> If you can't explain your product in one sentence, it's too complicated for v1.</div></li>
    <li><div class="tip-num">3</div><div><strong>How will people find it?</strong> Even the best product is useless if nobody knows it exists. Think distribution from day one.</div></li>
    <li><div class="tip-num">4</div><div><strong>What does "done" look like?</strong> Define your MVP scope. Ship it, get feedback, then improve. Don't build in the dark.</div></li>
    <li><div class="tip-num">5</div><div><strong>Can you build it in a weekend?</strong> If yes, great &mdash; start now. If not, cut scope until you can. Momentum matters more than perfection.</div></li>
  </ul>
</div>

<!-- GATE FORM -->
<div class="gate-wrap" id="gate-section">
  <div class="gate-card">
    <div class="gate-title">Unlock the full roadmap</div>
    <div class="gate-subtitle">6 phases. Every tool, every step, every decision. <strong>Free &mdash; no spam.</strong></div>
    <ul class="teaser-list">
      <li>Phase 1&ndash;6 with specific tools, stacks &amp; deployment options</li>
      <li>What to build first and what to skip</li>
      <li>AI integration guide &mdash; APIs, rules, cost control</li>
      <li>Copy as plain text &mdash; paste into Notion, share with your team</li>
    </ul>
    <form id="gateForm" novalidate>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="gate-name">Your Name *</label>
        <input type="text" id="gate-name" name="name" placeholder="Rahul Sharma" required autocomplete="name" />
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="gate-email">Email Address *</label>
        <input type="email" id="gate-email" name="email" placeholder="rahul@gmail.com" required autocomplete="email" />
        <div class="field-status" id="emailStatus"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="gate-phone">Phone Number *</label>
        <input type="tel" id="gate-phone" name="phone" placeholder="+91 98765 43210 or +1 555 123 4567" required autocomplete="tel" />
        <div class="field-status" id="phoneStatus"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="gate-building">What are you building? *</label>
        <input type="text" id="gate-building" name="building" placeholder="e.g. AI chatbot for restaurants" required />
      </div>
      <div class="cf-turnstile" data-sitekey="0x4AAAAAACgSvRvZpT5d_Ab5" data-theme="dark" data-callback="onTurnstileSuccess" data-expired-callback="onTurnstileExpired" style="margin-bottom:1rem;display:flex;justify-content:center"></div>
      <div class="error-msg" id="formError"></div>
      <button type="submit" class="btn-unlock" id="unlockBtn" disabled>Fill all fields to unlock</button>
      <p class="gate-privacy"><span>&#128274; Your info is safe. No spam, unsubscribe anytime.</span></p>
    </form>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ROADMAP CONTENT -->
<div id="roadmap-content">
  <div class="unlock-banner">
    <div class="unlock-icon">&#127881;</div>
    <div class="unlock-text">
      <strong>Hey <span id="userName">there</span>, your roadmap is ready!</strong>
      <span>Click any phase to expand. Use the copy button to save it as plain text.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="copy-bar">
    <button class="btn-copy" id="copyBtn">
      <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V4a2 2 0 012-2h9a2 2 0 012 2v1"/></svg>
      Copy as Text
    </button>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 1 -->
  <div class="phase-card phase-purple">
    <div class="phase-header">
      <div class="phase-color"></div>
      <div class="phase-num">1</div>
      <div class="phase-info">
        <div class="phase-title">Idea & Planning</div>
        <div class="phase-tag">Define what you're building and for whom</div>
      </div>
      <svg class="phase-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-body"><div class="phase-inner">
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Decide</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Who is it for? Define your target user clearly</li>
          <li>What is the one core feature? Not five, just one</li>
          <li>Web or mobile? Pick one to start</li>
          <li>Free or paid? Decide the model upfront</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Tools</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Figma &mdash; wireframe your screens (free tier)</li>
          <li>Notion &mdash; write your spec and track tasks</li>
          <li>Claude / ChatGPT &mdash; validate your idea, get feedback</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 2 -->
  <div class="phase-card phase-blue">
    <div class="phase-header">
      <div class="phase-color"></div>
      <div class="phase-num">2</div>
      <div class="phase-info">
        <div class="phase-title">Pick Your Stack</div>
        <div class="phase-tag">Choose the right tools for the job</div>
      </div>
      <svg class="phase-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-body"><div class="phase-inner">
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Web</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>React + Vite &mdash; fast dev, great ecosystem</li>
          <li>Tailwind CSS &mdash; utility-first, ship faster</li>
          <li>Vercel Serverless Functions &mdash; backend without servers</li>
          <li>Neon Postgres &mdash; serverless database, generous free tier</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Mobile</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>React Native + Expo &mdash; one codebase, both platforms</li>
          <li>Or PWA &mdash; web app that works like a native app, no app store needed</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 3 -->
  <div class="phase-card phase-green">
    <div class="phase-header">
      <div class="phase-color"></div>
      <div class="phase-num">3</div>
      <div class="phase-info">
        <div class="phase-title">Build MVP</div>
        <div class="phase-tag">Ship the smallest useful version</div>
      </div>
      <svg class="phase-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-body"><div class="phase-inner">
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Must-haves</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Auth &mdash; Google login (easiest, users trust it)</li>
          <li>One core flow &mdash; the main thing your product does, end to end</li>
          <li>Data save &mdash; user actions persist across sessions</li>
          <li>Basic UI &mdash; clean, functional, doesn't need to be beautiful yet</li>
          <li>Error handling &mdash; don't let users hit broken screens</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Skip for now</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Admin dashboard</li>
          <li>Email notifications</li>
          <li>Dark mode</li>
          <li>Animations and micro-interactions</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 4 -->
  <div class="phase-card phase-amber">
    <div class="phase-header">
      <div class="phase-color"></div>
      <div class="phase-num">4</div>
      <div class="phase-info">
        <div class="phase-title">Deploy</div>
        <div class="phase-tag">Get it live on the internet</div>
      </div>
      <svg class="phase-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-body"><div class="phase-inner">
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Frontend</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Vercel &mdash; free, auto-deploys from GitHub</li>
          <li>Cloudflare Pages &mdash; free, fast global CDN</li>
          <li>Netlify &mdash; free, good for static sites</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Backend</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Vercel Serverless Functions</li>
          <li>Cloudflare Workers &mdash; 100K req/day free</li>
          <li>Railway &mdash; easy full-stack deploys</li>
          <li>AWS App Runner &mdash; containers made simple</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Database</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Neon &mdash; serverless Postgres, free tier</li>
          <li>Supabase &mdash; Postgres + auth + storage, free tier</li>
          <li>Cloudflare D1 &mdash; SQLite at the edge, 5GB free</li>
          <li>PlanetScale &mdash; MySQL, generous free tier</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 5 -->
  <div class="phase-card phase-coral">
    <div class="phase-header">
      <div class="phase-color"></div>
      <div class="phase-num">5</div>
      <div class="phase-info">
        <div class="phase-title">Domain & Essentials</div>
        <div class="phase-tag">Make it real and professional</div>
      </div>
      <svg class="phase-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-body"><div class="phase-inner">
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Domain</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Cloudflare Registrar &mdash; cheapest, no markup pricing</li>
          <li>GoDaddy &mdash; popular, frequent sales</li>
          <li>Namecheap &mdash; affordable, good UI</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Must-add</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>GA4 &mdash; know who's using your product and how</li>
          <li>Sentry &mdash; catch errors before your users report them</li>
          <li>Privacy Policy &mdash; legally required, use a generator</li>
          <li>Razorpay / Stripe &mdash; if you're charging, set up payments</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Phase 6 -->
  <div class="phase-card phase-deep-purple">
    <div class="phase-header">
      <div class="phase-color"></div>
      <div class="phase-num">6</div>
      <div class="phase-info">
        <div class="phase-title">AI Integration</div>
        <div class="phase-tag">Optional &mdash; add intelligence to your product</div>
      </div>
      <svg class="phase-chevron" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="6 9 12 15 18 9"/></svg>
    </div>
    <div class="phase-body"><div class="phase-inner">
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">APIs</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Claude Haiku &mdash; fast, cheap, great for chat</li>
          <li>Claude Sonnet &mdash; complex reasoning, analysis</li>
          <li>GPT-4o &mdash; multimodal, strong general-purpose</li>
          <li>Gemini Flash &mdash; fast, good free tier</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-section">
        <div class="phase-section-title">Rules</div>
        <ul class="phase-list">
          <li>Never expose API keys in frontend code</li>
          <li>Proxy all AI calls through your backend</li>
          <li>Cache responses where possible to save cost</li>
          <li>Rate limit per user to prevent abuse</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div></div>
  </div>

  <!-- Veyra CTA -->
  <div class="veyra-cta">
    <h3>See this roadmap <em style="font-family:var(--serif);color:#7C6FE9">in action</em></h3>
    <p>Veyra is a real AI product built exactly following this roadmap &mdash; conversational AI that captures leads for small businesses, deployed on AWS, built in days.</p>
    <a href="https://theveyra.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-veyra">Try Veyra &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</div>

<script is:inline src="/form-utils.js"></script>
<script is:inline>
  // Check sessionStorage for returning visitors
  if (sessionStorage.getItem("roadmap_unlocked") === "true") {
    var saved = localStorage.getItem("roadmap_user");
    if (saved) {
      try { showRoadmap(JSON.parse(saved).name); } catch (e) {}
    }
  }

  // Init form with OyeNinoForm (form-utils.js)
  new OyeNinoForm({
    formId: "gateForm",
    emailId: "gate-email",
    phoneId: "gate-phone",
    nameId: "gate-name",
    btnId: "unlockBtn",
    statusId: "emailStatus",
    phoneStatusId: "phoneStatus",
    errorId: "formError",
    formName: "roadmap_gate",
    source: "roadmap_page",
    requiredFields: ["name", "email", "phone", "building"],
    btnTexts: {
      ready: "<span>&#128640;</span> Unlock Full Roadmap — Free",
      turnstile: "Verify you're human first \u2191",
      email: "Enter a valid email first",
      phone: "Enter a valid phone number",
      fields: "Fill all fields to unlock",
      submitting: "<span>&#8987;</span> Submitting..."
    },
    onSuccess: function (payload) {
      sessionStorage.setItem("roadmap_unlocked", "true");
      localStorage.setItem("roadmap_user", JSON.stringify({
        name: payload.name,
        email: payload.email,
        building: payload.building
      }));
      showRoadmap(payload.name);
    }
  });

  function showRoadmap(name) {
    var gate = document.getElementById("gate-section");
    var why = document.getElementById("why-section");
    var tips = document.getElementById("tips-section");
    gate.style.transition = "opacity 0.4s ease, transform 0.4s ease";
    gate.style.opacity = "0";
    gate.style.transform = "translateY(-10px)";
    setTimeout(function () {
      gate.style.display = "none";
      why.style.display = "none";
      tips.style.display = "none";
      var firstName = (name || "there").split(" ")[0];
      document.getElementById("userName").textContent = firstName;
      var content = document.getElementById("roadmap-content");
      content.classList.add("unlocked");
      content.scrollIntoView({ behavior: "smooth", block: "start" });
    }, 400);
  }

  function togglePhase(card) {
    card.classList.toggle("open");
  }

  // Attach click handlers to phase cards
  document.querySelectorAll(".phase-card").forEach(function(card) {
    card.querySelector(".phase-header").addEventListener("click", function() {
      togglePhase(card);
    });
  });

  // Copy roadmap
  document.getElementById("copyBtn").addEventListener("click", function() {
    var text =
      "BUILD YOUR PRODUCT \u2014 STEP-BY-STEP ROADMAP\n" +
      "by Himanshu (@oye.nino)\n" +
      "==================================================\n\n" +
      "PHASE 1 \u2014 IDEA & PLANNING\n------------------------------\nDecide:\n  - Who is it for? Define your target user clearly\n  - What is the one core feature? Not five, just one\n  - Web or mobile? Pick one to start\n  - Free or paid? Decide the model upfront\nTools:\n  - Figma \u2014 wireframe your screens (free tier)\n  - Notion \u2014 write your spec and track tasks\n  - Claude / ChatGPT \u2014 validate your idea, get feedback\n\n" +
      "PHASE 2 \u2014 PICK YOUR STACK\n------------------------------\nWeb:\n  - React + Vite \u2014 fast dev, great ecosystem\n  - Tailwind CSS \u2014 utility-first, ship faster\n  - Vercel Serverless Functions \u2014 backend without servers\n  - Neon Postgres \u2014 serverless database, generous free tier\nMobile:\n  - React Native + Expo \u2014 one codebase, both platforms\n  - Or PWA \u2014 web app that works like a native app, no app store needed\n\n" +
      "PHASE 3 \u2014 BUILD MVP\n------------------------------\nMust-haves:\n  - Auth \u2014 Google login (easiest, users trust it)\n  - One core flow \u2014 the main thing your product does, end to end\n  - Data save \u2014 user actions persist across sessions\n  - Basic UI \u2014 clean, functional, doesn't need to be beautiful yet\n  - Error handling \u2014 don't let users hit broken screens\nSkip for now:\n  - Admin dashboard\n  - Email notifications\n  - Dark mode\n  - Animations and micro-interactions\n\n" +
      "PHASE 4 \u2014 DEPLOY\n------------------------------\nFrontend:\n  - Vercel \u2014 free, auto-deploys from GitHub\n  - Cloudflare Pages \u2014 free, fast global CDN\n  - Netlify \u2014 free, good for static sites\nBackend:\n  - Vercel Serverless Functions\n  - Cloudflare Workers \u2014 100K req/day free\n  - Railway \u2014 easy full-stack deploys\n  - AWS App Runner \u2014 containers made simple\nDatabase:\n  - Neon \u2014 serverless Postgres, free tier\n  - Supabase \u2014 Postgres + auth + storage, free tier\n  - Cloudflare D1 \u2014 SQLite at the edge, 5GB free\n  - PlanetScale \u2014 MySQL, generous free tier\n\n" +
      "PHASE 5 \u2014 DOMAIN & ESSENTIALS\n------------------------------\nDomain:\n  - Cloudflare Registrar \u2014 cheapest, no markup pricing\n  - GoDaddy \u2014 popular, frequent sales\n  - Namecheap \u2014 affordable, good UI\nMust-add:\n  - GA4 \u2014 know who's using your product and how\n  - Sentry \u2014 catch errors before your users report them\n  - Privacy Policy \u2014 legally required, use a generator\n  - Razorpay / Stripe \u2014 if you're charging, set up payments\n\n" +
      "PHASE 6 \u2014 AI INTEGRATION (OPTIONAL)\n------------------------------\nAPIs:\n  - Claude Haiku \u2014 fast, cheap, great for chat\n  - Claude Sonnet \u2014 complex reasoning, analysis\n  - GPT-4o \u2014 multimodal, strong general-purpose\n  - Gemini Flash \u2014 fast, good free tier\nRules:\n  - Never expose API keys in frontend code\n  - Proxy all AI calls through your backend\n  - Cache responses where possible to save cost\n  - Rate limit per user to prevent abuse\n\n" +
      "==================================================\n" +
      "See this roadmap in action: https://theveyra.app/\n" +
      "More free prompts: https://oyenino.com/prompts.html\n";

    var btn = document.getElementById("copyBtn");
    navigator.clipboard.writeText(text).then(function () {
      btn.innerHTML = '<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg> Copied!';
      btn.classList.add("copied");
      if (typeof gtag === "function") gtag("event", "roadmap_copied");
      setTimeout(function () {
        btn.innerHTML = '<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="9" y="9" width="13" height="13" rx="2"/><path d="M5 15H4a2 2 0 01-2-2V4a2 2 0 012-2h9a2 2 0 012 2v1"/></svg> Copy as Text';
        btn.classList.remove("copied");
      }, 2000);
    });
  });
</script>

</SubPageLayout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .page-hero{padding:9rem 2rem 3rem;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;text-align:center;position:relative}
  .hero-glow{position:absolute;top:0;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:700px;height:400px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse,rgba(124,111,233,0.12) 0%,transparent 65%);pointer-events:none;filter:blur(80px);animation:breathe 6s ease-in-out infinite}
  .page-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:0.5rem;font-size:0.78rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--accent);margin-bottom:1.5rem;font-weight:500;animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards}
  .pulse{width:7px;height:7px;background:var(--accent);border-radius:50%;animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
  .page-hero h1{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:clamp(2.2rem,6vw,3.5rem);font-weight:400;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.03em;margin-bottom:1.25rem;animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 0.1s;opacity:0}
  .page-hero h1 em{font-style:italic;color:#7C6FE9}
  .page-hero p{font-size:1.05rem;color:var(--text-mid);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto;font-weight:300;line-height:1.75;animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 0.2s;opacity:0}

  /* Why section */
  .why-section{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto 3rem;padding:0 2rem;animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 0.3s;opacity:0}
  .why-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(220px,1fr));gap:1rem}
  .why-card{background:var(--bg-card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;padding:1.5rem;transition:border-color var(--transition)}
  .why-card:hover{border-color:var(--border-hover)}
  .why-icon{font-size:1.5rem;margin-bottom:0.75rem}
  .why-card h3{font-size:0.9rem;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:0.4rem;color:var(--text)}
  .why-card p{font-size:0.82rem;color:var(--text-muted);font-weight:300;line-height:1.6}

  /* Planning tips */
  .tips-section{max-width:800px;margin:0 auto 3.5rem;padding:0 2rem;animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease forwards 0.35s;opacity:0}
  .tips-title{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:1.4rem;font-weight:400;text-align:center;margin-bottom:1.5rem}
